ZH: 传染病是通过病原体传播的。
EN: Infectious diseases are spread through pathogens.
ZH: 我感到有些不舒服，可能传染了感冒。
EN: I feel a bit uncomfortable, I might have caught a cold.
ZH: 许多细菌会传染给人类。
EN: Many bacteria can be transmitted to humans.
ZH: 非洲的传染病问题一直很棘手。
EN: Infectious diseases have always been a serious problem in Africa.
ZH: 这种病毒只能通过血液传染。
EN: This virus can only be transmitted through blood.
ZH: 他的感染已经传染给了其他人。
EN: His infection has already been passed on to others.
ZH: 尽量避免接触传染源可以减少感染风险。
EN: Avoiding contact with the source of infection can reduce the risk of getting infected.
ZH: 这些物品已被证实能够传染病菌。
EN: These items have been proven to be able to transmit disease-causing bacteria.
ZH: 传染病的扩散速度非常快。
EN: Infectious diseases spread rapidly.
ZH: 更频繁地洗手能够降低传染的可能性。
EN: Washing hands more frequently can reduce the likelihood of transmission.
ZH: 孩子们容易相互传染疾病。
EN: Children are prone to infecting each other with diseases.
ZH: 他被确诊患有高度传染性疾病。
EN: He has been diagnosed with a highly contagious disease.
ZH: 传染病的蔓延使政府采取了紧急措施。
EN: The spread of infectious diseases has led the government to take emergency measures.
ZH: 那个城市的传染率已经下降了。
EN: The infection rate in that city has already decreased.
ZH: 所有的医疗工作者都应该对传染病有所了解。
EN: All healthcare workers should have knowledge of infectious diseases.
ZH: 他们在试验室中研究如何传染病毒。
EN: They study how to transmit viruses in the laboratory.
ZH: 传染病的预防非常重要。
EN: Prevention of infectious diseases is crucial.
ZH: 疫苗有助于防止传染病的扩散。
EN: Vaccines help prevent the spread of infectious diseases.
ZH: 这个地区的传染病爆发导致了大量的死亡。
EN: The outbreak of infectious diseases in this region has led to a high number of deaths.
ZH: 学校暂时关闭以防止疾病的传染。
EN: The school is temporarily closed to prevent the transmission of diseases.
